00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:24.770
So chemical peels are used for multiple different
concerns.

00:00:24.770 --> 00:00:40.470
A patient may choose a specific chemical peel
for a different concern, whether it be mild

00:00:40.470 --> 00:00:46.379
pigmentation, either, acne scars that they
are concerned about, or just rejuvenation

00:00:46.379 --> 00:00:47.390
of the skin.

00:00:47.390 --> 00:00:52.100
The different types of chemical peels that
we have in the office do vary.

00:00:52.100 --> 00:00:55.830
Procedure time for a chemical peels can take
anywhere from about thirty minutes.

00:00:55.830 --> 00:01:01.750
It’s a fairly quick procedure, it’s a
non-invasive procedure.

00:01:01.750 --> 00:01:07.450
Some patients can experience, you know, some
warming to the skin, and, or stinging or burning-like

00:01:07.450 --> 00:01:08.729
sensation.

00:01:08.729 --> 00:01:14.190
There is a fan used to calm down the sensation
to make it a lot more tolerable for the patient.

00:01:14.190 --> 00:01:16.549
For the most part, it’s fairly comfortable.

00:01:16.549 --> 00:01:22.409
With each patient we will tailor the specific
treatment to them, which can depend on the

00:01:22.409 --> 00:01:25.170
degree of downtime as well with each chemical
peel.

00:01:25.170 --> 00:01:32.659
The more aggressive the peel, the more downtime
which can include flaking and peeling and

00:01:32.659 --> 00:01:38.130
redness, which can last up to a week’s time,
whereas the mild chemical peels can cause

00:01:38.130 --> 00:01:42.950
just a little bit of redness or flaking for
just a couple of days.

00:01:42.950 --> 00:01:49.430
So the end result with the chemical peels
is to give the patient a nice refreshed glow

00:01:49.430 --> 00:01:56.340
to the skin, help with mild pigmentation,
also you know, if they have those deeper,

00:01:56.340 --> 00:02:01.649
pitted acne scars, if we’ve helped to smooth
them out a little bit more, and you know reduce

00:02:01.649 --> 00:02:07.299
the appearance with the chemical peels, make
people to feel better about themselves, and

00:02:07.299 --> 00:02:09.700
target those concerns that bother them.

